📌 CodSoft Internship - Python Programming

Task: Password Generator
Internship: CodSoft Python Programming Internship

📖 Project Description

This project is a Password Generator developed using Python. It generates secure and random passwords based on the user's preferred password length and complexity level.

The program allows users to choose from three different password strength options and creates a random password using Python's built-in random and string modules.

✨ Features
Generates random passwords of any desired length.
Offers three levels of password complexity:
Weak – Alphabetic characters (A–Z, a–z)
Strong – Letters and numbers
Very Strong – Letters, numbers, and special characters
Validates user input for password length.
Handles invalid inputs gracefully using exception handling.
Produces a secure random password every time the program runs.
